main event: Two circles of light were observed in Warrenton, NC on 9th October 1950, with each circle trying to go near the other.
interesting points: The report was sourced from Col. and other (Newspaper RPT.), indicating multiple witnesses.
The UFO sighting occurred on the ground, suggesting a close encounter.
The circles of light appeared to be interacting with each other, indicating potential intelligent movement.
The report is from Project Blue Book, a U.S. Air Force study of UFOs.
The behavior of the circles of light is unusual and warrants further investigation.
